item.title: 10 page pdf into word
item.description:
https://www.freelancer.com/projects/word/Type-Page-PDF-into-Word-38585368/details

I’m looking for someone to transcribe a 10 page PDF file into a Microsoft Word document.

Requirements:

  • The final document should be in standard text formatting. No need for any special styles, just clear and neat typing.
  • The PDF file contains text only, so no charts or images are needed.

Ideal skills and experience for the job include:

  • Proficiency in Microsoft Word
  • Excellent typing skills
  • Attention to detail to ensure accurate transcription.

File: [Annexure-I](/files/Annexure- I.pdf)
